{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I think it was in my second grade that I was caught"},{"time":3000,"text":"drawing the bust of a nude by Michelangelo."},{"time":6000,"text":"I was sent straight away to my school principal,"},{"time":9000,"text":"and my school principal, a sweet nun,"},{"time":12000,"text":"looked at my book with disgust,"},{"time":15000,"text":"flipped through the pages, saw all the nudes --"},{"time":18000,"text":"you know, I'd been seeing my mother draw nudes and I'd copy her --"},{"time":21000,"text":"and the nun slapped me on my face and said,"},{"time":23000,"text":"\"Sweet Jesus, this kid has already begun.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":26000,"text":"I had no clue what she was talking about,"},{"time":28000,"text":"but it was convincing enough for me never to draw again"},{"time":34000,"text":"until the ninth grade."},{"time":36000,"text":"Thanks to a really boring lecture,"},{"time":38000,"text":"I started caricaturing my teachers in school."},{"time":41000,"text":"And, you know, I got a lot of popularity."},{"time":44000,"text":"I don't play sports. I'm really bad at sports."},{"time":46000,"text":"I don't have the fanciest gadgets at home."},{"time":49000,"text":"I'm not on top of the class."},{"time":51000,"text":"So for me, cartooning gave me a sense of identity."},{"time":54000,"text":"I got popular, but I was scared I'd get caught again."},{"time":57000,"text":"So what I did was I quickly put together"},{"time":59000,"text":"a collage of all the teachers I had drawn,"},{"time":63000,"text":"glorified my school principal, put him right on top,"},{"time":66000,"text":"and gifted it to him."},{"time":68000,"text":"He had a good laugh at the other teachers"},{"time":70000,"text":"and put it up on the notice board."},{"time":72000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":74000,"text":"This is a part of that."},{"time":76000,"text":"And I became a school hero."},{"time":78000,"text":"All my seniors knew me. I felt really special."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"I have to tell you a little bit about my family."},{"time":84000,"text":"That's my mother. I love her to bits."},{"time":87000,"text":"She's the one who taught me how to draw and, more importantly, how to love."},{"time":90000,"text":"She's a bit of a hippie."},{"time":92000,"text":"She said, \"Don't say that,\" but I'm saying it anyway."},{"time":95000,"text":"The rest of my family are boring academics,"},{"time":98000,"text":"busy collecting Ivy League decals for our classic Ambassador car."},{"time":101000,"text":"My father's a little different."},{"time":103000,"text":"My father believed in a holistic approach to living,"},{"time":107000,"text":"and, you know, every time he taught us,"},{"time":109000,"text":"he'd say, \"I hate these books,"},{"time":111000,"text":"because these books are hijacked by Industrial Revolution.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":114000,"text":"While he still held that worldview, I was 16,"},{"time":117000,"text":"I got the best lawyer in town,"},{"time":119000,"text":"my older brother Karthik,"},{"time":121000,"text":"and I sat him down, and I said, \"Pa,"},{"time":123000,"text":"from today onwards I've decided"},{"time":125000,"text":"I'm going to be disciplined,"},{"time":127000,"text":"I'm going to be curious,"},{"time":129000,"text":"I'm going to learn something new every day,"},{"time":131000,"text":"I'm going to be very hard working,"},{"time":133000,"text":"and I'm not going to depend on you"},{"time":135000,"text":"emotionally or financially.\""},{"time":137000,"text":"And he was very impressed. He was all tearing up. Ready to hug me."},{"time":140000,"text":"And I said, \"Hold that thought.\""},{"time":142000,"text":"I said, \"Can I quit school then?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"But, to cut a long story short,"},{"time":147000,"text":"I quit school to pursue a career as a cartoonist."},{"time":150000,"text":"I must have done about 30,000 caricatures."},{"time":152000,"text":"I would do birthday parties, weddings, divorces,"},{"time":155000,"text":"anything for anyone who wanted to use my services."},{"time":158000,"text":"But, most importantly, while I was traveling,"},{"time":161000,"text":"I taught children cartooning,"},{"time":163000,"text":"and in exchange, I learned how to be spontaneous."},{"time":165000,"text":"And mad and crazy and fun."},{"time":168000,"text":"When I started teaching them, I said let me start doing this professionally."},{"time":171000,"text":"When I was 18 I started my own school."},{"time":174000,"text":"However, an 18 year-old trying to start a school"},{"time":177000,"text":"is not easy unless you have a big patron"},{"time":179000,"text":"or a big supporter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"So I was flipping through the pages of the Times of India"},{"time":184000,"text":"when I saw that the Prime Minister of India"},{"time":186000,"text":"was visiting my home town, Bangalore."},{"time":190000,"text":"And, you know, just like how"},{"time":192000,"text":"every cartoonist knows Bush here,"},{"time":194000,"text":"and if you had to meet Bush,"},{"time":196000,"text":"it would be the funnest thing because"},{"time":198000,"text":"his face was a cartoonist's delight."},{"time":200000,"text":"I had to meet my Prime Minister."},{"time":202000,"text":"I went to the place where"},{"time":204000,"text":"his helicopter was about to land."},{"time":206000,"text":"I saw layers of security."},{"time":208000,"text":"I caricatured my way through three layers"},{"time":211000,"text":"by just impressing the guards,"},{"time":213000,"text":"but I got stuck. I got stuck at the third."},{"time":216000,"text":"And what happened was, to my luck,"},{"time":218000,"text":"I saw a nuclear scientist"},{"time":220000,"text":"at whose party I had done cartoons."},{"time":222000,"text":"I ran up to him, and said, \"Hello, sir. How do you do?\""},{"time":224000,"text":"He said, \"What are you doing here, Raghava?\""},{"time":226000,"text":"I said, \"I'm here to meet the Prime Minister.\""},{"time":228000,"text":"He said, \"Oh, so am I.\""},{"time":230000,"text":"I hopped into his car, and off we went"},{"time":232000,"text":"through the remaining layers of security."},{"time":234000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":236000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":238000,"text":"I sat him down, I caricatured him,"},{"time":240000,"text":"and since then I've caricatured hundreds of celebrities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"This is one I remember fondly."},{"time":245000,"text":"Salman Rushdie was pissed-off I think"},{"time":247000,"text":"because I altered the map of New York, if you notice."},{"time":249000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":253000,"text":"Anyway, the next slide I'm about to show you --"},{"time":256000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":259000,"text":"Should I just turn that off?"},{"time":261000,"text":"The next slide I'm about to show you,"},{"time":263000,"text":"is a little more serious."},{"time":265000,"text":"I was hesitant to include this in my presentation"},{"time":268000,"text":"because this cartoon was published"},{"time":270000,"text":"soon after 9/11."},{"time":272000,"text":"What was, for me, a very naive observation,"},{"time":275000,"text":"turned out to be a disaster."},{"time":277000,"text":"That evening, I came home to hundreds of hate mails,"},{"time":281000,"text":"hundreds of people telling me how they"},{"time":283000,"text":"could have lived another day without seeing this."},{"time":285000,"text":"I was also asked to leave the organization,"},{"time":287000,"text":"a cartoonists' organization in America,"},{"time":290000,"text":"that for me was my lifeline."},{"time":292000,"text":"That's when I realized, you know, cartoons are really powerful,"},{"time":295000,"text":"art comes with responsibility."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297000,"text":"Anyway, what I did was I decided"},{"time":299000,"text":"that I need to take a break."},{"time":301000,"text":"I quit my job at the papers, I closed my school,"},{"time":304000,"text":"and I wrapped up my pencils and my brushes and inks,"},{"time":307000,"text":"and I decided to go traveling."},{"time":309000,"text":"When I went traveling, I remember,"},{"time":311000,"text":"I met this fabulous old man,"},{"time":314000,"text":"who I met when I was caricaturing,"},{"time":316000,"text":"who turned out to be an artist, in Italy."},{"time":319000,"text":"He invited me to his studio. He said, \"Come and visit.\""},{"time":322000,"text":"When I went, I saw the ghastliest thing ever."},{"time":325000,"text":"I saw this dead, naked effigy of himself"},{"time":328000,"text":"hanging from the ceiling."},{"time":330000,"text":"I said, \"Oh, my God. What is that?\""},{"time":332000,"text":"And I asked him, and he said,"},{"time":334000,"text":"\"Oh, that thing? In the night, I die."},{"time":336000,"text":"In the morning, I am born again.\""},{"time":339000,"text":"I thought he was koo koo,"},{"time":341000,"text":"but something about that really stuck."},{"time":343000,"text":"I loved it. I thought there was something really beautiful about that."},{"time":346000,"text":"So I said, \"I am dead, so I need to be born again.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":349000,"text":"So, I wanted to be a painter like him,"},{"time":352000,"text":"except, I don't know how to paint."},{"time":354000,"text":"So, I tried going to the art store."},{"time":356000,"text":"You know, there are a hundred types of brushes."},{"time":359000,"text":"Forget it, they will confuse you"},{"time":361000,"text":"even if you know how to draw."},{"time":363000,"text":"So I decided, I'm going to learn to paint by myself."},{"time":365000,"text":"I'm going to show you a very quick clip"},{"time":367000,"text":"to show you how I painted and a little bit"},{"time":369000,"text":"about my city, Bangalore."},{"time":372000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":402000,"text":"They had to be larger than life."},{"time":404000,"text":"Everything had to be larger. The next painting was even bigger."},{"time":407000,"text":"And even bigger."},{"time":409000,"text":"And for me it was, I had to dance while I painted."},{"time":411000,"text":"It was so exciting."},{"time":413000,"text":"Except, I even started painting dancers."},{"time":415000,"text":"Here for example is a Flamenco dancer,"},{"time":417000,"text":"except there was one problem."},{"time":420000,"text":"I didn't know the dance form, so I started following them,"},{"time":423000,"text":"and I made some money,"},{"time":425000,"text":"sold my paintings and would rush off"},{"time":427000,"text":"to France or Spain and work with them."},{"time":429000,"text":"That's Pepe Linares, the renowned Flamenco singer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433000,"text":"But I had one problem, my paintings never danced."},{"time":436000,"text":"As much energy as I put into them"},{"time":438000,"text":"while making them, they never danced."},{"time":441000,"text":"So I decided -- I had this crazy epiphany at two in the morning."},{"time":444000,"text":"I called my friends, painted on their bodies,"},{"time":446000,"text":"and had them dance in front of a painting."},{"time":449000,"text":"And, all of a sudden, my paintings came alive."},{"time":452000,"text":"And then I was fortunate enough"},{"time":454000,"text":"to actually perform this in California with Velocity Circus."},{"time":457000,"text":"And I sat like you guys there in the audience."},{"time":460000,"text":"And I saw my work come alive."},{"time":462000,"text":"You know, normally you work in isolation,"},{"time":464000,"text":"and you show at a gallery,"},{"time":466000,"text":"but here, the work was coming alive,"},{"time":469000,"text":"and it had some other artists working with me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471000,"text":"The collaborative effort was fabulous."},{"time":473000,"text":"I said, I'm going to collaborate with anybody and everybody I meet."},{"time":477000,"text":"I started doing fashion."},{"time":479000,"text":"This is a fashion show we held in London."},{"time":481000,"text":"The best collaboration, of course, is with children."},{"time":484000,"text":"They are ruthless, they are honest,"},{"time":487000,"text":"but they're full of energy and fun."},{"time":489000,"text":"This is a work, a library I designed for the Robin Hood Foundation."},{"time":494000,"text":"And I must say, I spent time in the Bronx"},{"time":496000,"text":"working with these kids."},{"time":498000,"text":"And, in exchange for me working with them,"},{"time":500000,"text":"they taught me how to be cool."},{"time":502000,"text":"I don't think I've succeeded, but they've taught me."},{"time":504000,"text":"They said, \"Stop saying sorry. Say, my bad.\""},{"time":507000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512000,"text":"Then I said, all this is good,"},{"time":514000,"text":"but I want to paint like a real painter."},{"time":517000,"text":"American education is so expensive."},{"time":520000,"text":"I was in India, and I was walking down the streets,"},{"time":523000,"text":"and I saw a billboard painter."},{"time":525000,"text":"And these guys paint humongous paintings,"},{"time":529000,"text":"and they look really good."},{"time":531000,"text":"And I wondered how they did it from so close."},{"time":534000,"text":"So, one day I had the opportunity to meet one of these guys,"},{"time":536000,"text":"and I said, \"How do you paint like that? Who taught you?\""},{"time":539000,"text":"And he said, \"Oh, it's very easy. I can teach you,"},{"time":542000,"text":"but we're leaving the city,"},{"time":544000,"text":"because billboard painters are a dying,"},{"time":546000,"text":"extinct bunch of artists,"},{"time":549000,"text":"because digital printing has totally replaced them and hijacked them.\""},{"time":552000,"text":"I said, in exchange for education in how to paint,"},{"time":555000,"text":"I will support them, and I started a company."},{"time":558000,"text":"And since then, I've been painting all over the place."},{"time":561000,"text":"This is a painting I did of my wife in my apartment."},{"time":564000,"text":"This is another painting."},{"time":566000,"text":"And, in fact, I started painting on anything,"},{"time":568000,"text":"and started sending them around town."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570000,"text":"Since I mentioned my wife, the most important collaboration"},{"time":573000,"text":"has been with her, Netra."},{"time":575000,"text":"Netra and I met when she was 18."},{"time":578000,"text":"I must have been 19 and a half then,"},{"time":581000,"text":"and it was love at first sight."},{"time":583000,"text":"I lived in India. She lived in America."},{"time":585000,"text":"She'd come every two months to visit me,"},{"time":588000,"text":"and then I said I'm the man,"},{"time":591000,"text":"I'm the man, and I have to reciprocate."},{"time":595000,"text":"I have to travel seven oceans, and I have to come and see you."},{"time":598000,"text":"I did that twice, and I went broke."},{"time":602000,"text":"So then I said, \"Nets, what do I do?\""},{"time":604000,"text":"She said, \"Why don't you send me your paintings?"},{"time":606000,"text":"My dad knows a bunch of rich guys."},{"time":608000,"text":"We'll try and con them into buying it,"},{"time":610000,"text":"and then...\""},{"time":612000,"text":"But it turned out, after I sent the works to her,"},{"time":615000,"text":"that her dad's friends,"},{"time":617000,"text":"like most of you, are geeks."},{"time":619000,"text":"I'm joking."},{"time":621000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":625000,"text":"No, they were really big geeks,"},{"time":627000,"text":"and they didn't know much about art."},{"time":630000,"text":"So Netra was stuck with 30 paintings of mine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":634000,"text":"So what we did was we rented a little van"},{"time":637000,"text":"and we drove all over the east coast trying to sell it."},{"time":641000,"text":"She contacted anyone and everyone"},{"time":643000,"text":"who was willing to buy my work."},{"time":645000,"text":"She made enough money, she sold off the whole collection"},{"time":648000,"text":"and made enough money to move me for four years"},{"time":650000,"text":"with lawyers, a company, everything,"},{"time":653000,"text":"and she became my manager."},{"time":655000,"text":"That's us in New York."},{"time":657000,"text":"Notice one thing,"},{"time":659000,"text":"we're equal here."},{"time":661000,"text":"Something happened along the line."},{"time":663000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":666000,"text":"But this brought me -- with Netra managing my career --"},{"time":668000,"text":"it brought me a lot of success."},{"time":670000,"text":"I was really happy. I thought of myself as a bit of a rockstar."},{"time":674000,"text":"I loved the attention."},{"time":677000,"text":"This is all the press we got, and we said,"},{"time":679000,"text":"it's time to celebrate."},{"time":681000,"text":"And I said that the best way to celebrate is to marry Netra."},{"time":684000,"text":"I said, \"Let's get married.\""},{"time":686000,"text":"And I said, \"Not just married. Let's invite everyone who's helped us,"},{"time":689000,"text":"all the people who bought our work.\""},{"time":692000,"text":"And you won't believe it, we put together a list of 7,000 people,"},{"time":695000,"text":"who had made a difference -- a ridiculous list,"},{"time":698000,"text":"but I was determined to bring them to India, so --"},{"time":700000,"text":"a lot of them were in India."},{"time":702000,"text":"150 artists volunteered to help me with my wedding."},{"time":706000,"text":"We had fashion designers, installation artists,"},{"time":710000,"text":"models, we had makeup artists, jewelry designers,"},{"time":714000,"text":"all kinds of people working with me"},{"time":716000,"text":"to make my wedding an art installation."},{"time":718000,"text":"And I had a special installation in tribute to my in-laws."},{"time":723000,"text":"I had the vegetable carvers work on that for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726000,"text":"But all this excitement led"},{"time":728000,"text":"to the press writing about us."},{"time":730000,"text":"We were in the papers, we're still in the news three years later,"},{"time":733000,"text":"but, unfortunately, something tragic happened right after."},{"time":738000,"text":"My mother fell very ill."},{"time":740000,"text":"I love my mother"},{"time":742000,"text":"and I was told all of a sudden that she was going to die."},{"time":745000,"text":"And they said you have to say bye to her,"},{"time":747000,"text":"you have to do what you have to do."},{"time":749000,"text":"And I was devastated."},{"time":751000,"text":"I had shows booked up for another year."},{"time":753000,"text":"I was on a high."},{"time":755000,"text":"And I couldn't. I could not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":757000,"text":"My life was not exuberant."},{"time":759000,"text":"I could not live this larger than life person."},{"time":762000,"text":"I started exploring the darker abscesses of the human mind."},{"time":766000,"text":"Of course, my work turned ugly,"},{"time":769000,"text":"but another thing happened."},{"time":772000,"text":"I lost all my audiences."},{"time":774000,"text":"The Bollywood stars who I would party with"},{"time":777000,"text":"and buy my work disappeared."},{"time":780000,"text":"The collectors, the friends, the press,"},{"time":782000,"text":"everyone said, \"Nice, but thank you.\""},{"time":785000,"text":"\"No thank you,\" was more like it."},{"time":787000,"text":"But I wanted people to actually"},{"time":789000,"text":"feel my work from their gut,"},{"time":791000,"text":"because I was painting it from my gut."},{"time":793000,"text":"If they wanted beauty,"},{"time":795000,"text":"I said, this is the beauty I'm willing to give you. It's politicized."},{"time":798000,"text":"Of course, none of them liked it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":800000,"text":"My works also turned autobiographical."},{"time":804000,"text":"At this point, something else happened."},{"time":807000,"text":"A very, very dear friend of mine"},{"time":809000,"text":"came out of the closet,"},{"time":811000,"text":"and in India at that time, it was illegal to be gay,"},{"time":814000,"text":"and it's disgusting to see how people respond to a gay person."},{"time":818000,"text":"I was very upset."},{"time":820000,"text":"I remember the time when my mother used to dress me up"},{"time":823000,"text":"as a little girl -- that's me there --"},{"time":826000,"text":"because she wanted a girl, and she has only boys."},{"time":829000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":836000,"text":"Anyway, I don't know what my friends are going to say after this talk."},{"time":840000,"text":"It's a secret."}]},{"cues":[{"time":842000,"text":"So, after this, my works turned a little violent."},{"time":848000,"text":"I talked about this masculinity that one need not perform."},{"time":852000,"text":"And I talked about the weakness of male sexuality."},{"time":855000,"text":"This time, not only did my collectors disappear,"},{"time":858000,"text":"the political activists decided to ban me"},{"time":862000,"text":"and to threaten me"},{"time":864000,"text":"and to forbid me from showing."},{"time":866000,"text":"It turned nasty, and I'm a bit of a chicken."},{"time":868000,"text":"I can't deal with any threat. This was a big threat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871000,"text":"So, I decided it was time"},{"time":874000,"text":"to end and go back home."},{"time":877000,"text":"This time I said let's try something different."},{"time":879000,"text":"I need to be reborn again."},{"time":881000,"text":"And I thought the best way, as most of you know who have children,"},{"time":884000,"text":"the best way to have a new lease on life,"},{"time":886000,"text":"is to have a child."},{"time":888000,"text":"I decided to have a child,"},{"time":890000,"text":"and before I did that, I quickly studied what can go wrong."},{"time":893000,"text":"How can a family get dysfunctional?"},{"time":896000,"text":"And Rudra was born."},{"time":898000,"text":"That's my little son."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900000,"text":"And two magical things happened after he was born."},{"time":902000,"text":"My mother miraculously recovered"},{"time":904000,"text":"after a serious operation,"},{"time":907000,"text":"and this man was elected president of this country."},{"time":911000,"text":"You know I sat at home and I watched."},{"time":913000,"text":"I teared up and I said that's where I want to be."},{"time":916000,"text":"So Netra and I wound up our life,"},{"time":919000,"text":"closed up everything we had,"},{"time":921000,"text":"and we decided to move to New York."},{"time":923000,"text":"And this was just eight months ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":925000,"text":"I moved back to New York, my work has changed."},{"time":927000,"text":"Everything about my work has become more whimsical."},{"time":931000,"text":"This one is called \"What the Fuck Was I Thinking?\""},{"time":934000,"text":"It talks about mental incest."},{"time":937000,"text":"You know, I may appear to be a very nice, clean, sweet boy."},{"time":941000,"text":"But I'm not. I'm capable of thinking anything."},{"time":944000,"text":"But I'm very civil in my action, I assure you."},{"time":947000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":950000,"text":"These are just different cartoons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":952000,"text":"And, before I go, I want to tell you a little story."},{"time":955000,"text":"I was talking to mother and father this morning,"},{"time":957000,"text":"and my dad said, \"I know you have so much you want to say,"},{"time":961000,"text":"but you have to talk about your work with children.\""},{"time":964000,"text":"So I said, okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":966000,"text":"I work with children all over the world,"},{"time":968000,"text":"and that's an entirely different talk,"},{"time":970000,"text":"but I want to leave you with one story"},{"time":972000,"text":"that really, really inspired me."},{"time":974000,"text":"I met Belinda when she was 16."},{"time":977000,"text":"I was 17."},{"time":979000,"text":"I was in Australia,"},{"time":981000,"text":"and Belinda had cancer,"},{"time":983000,"text":"and I was told she's not going to live very long."},{"time":987000,"text":"They, in fact, told me three weeks."},{"time":989000,"text":"I walk into her room, and there was a shy girl,"},{"time":991000,"text":"and she was bald, and she was trying to hide her baldness."},{"time":995000,"text":"I whipped out my pen, and I started drawing on her head"},{"time":998000,"text":"and I drew a crown for her."},{"time":1000000,"text":"And then, we started talking, and we spent a lovely time --"},{"time":1003000,"text":"I told her how I ended up in Australia,"},{"time":1005000,"text":"how I backpacked and who I conned, and how I got a ticket,"},{"time":1008000,"text":"and all the stories."},{"time":1010000,"text":"And I drew it out for her."},{"time":1012000,"text":"And then I left."},{"time":1015000,"text":"Belinda died"},{"time":1017000,"text":"and within a few days of her death,"},{"time":1023000,"text":"they published a book for her,"},{"time":1025000,"text":"and she used my cartoon on the cover."},{"time":1027000,"text":"And she wrote a little note, she said,"},{"time":1029000,"text":"\"Hey Rags, thank you for the magic carpet ride around the world.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1032000,"text":"For me, my art is my magic carpet ride."},{"time":1035000,"text":"I hope you will join me in this magic carpet ride,"},{"time":1038000,"text":"and touch children and be honest."},{"time":1040000,"text":"Thank you so much."},{"time":1042000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}